just return silently without any output."},{"type":"text","text":"All services normal — silent output as configured."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774670536280}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:d0fd6a2f-f302-4007-874b-0df8159f7a91","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: 每日复盘-教训反思","displayName":"Cron: 每日复盘-教训反思","updatedAt":1774670400008,"sessionId":"f407c099-02bd-457b-adf2-f7ab2f00c469","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":58626,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/f407c099-02bd-457b-adf2-f7ab2f00c469.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1774670400519,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted."}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774670580459}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd38c97a","parentId":"994e2d82","timestamp":"2026-03-28T04:03:11.646Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the sessions, the only sessions are cron jobs (all labeled with \"cron:\"), not user conversations. There are no recent user messages. Let me check if there are any active sessions from users by looking more broadly. The sessions_list shows only cron sessions. Let me also check for sessions with different kinds.\n\nActually, the cron task says \"查询 sessions_list\" - it returned 3 sessions, but these are all cron jobs (label contains \"Cron:\"). The task says if there's no active conversation (no user messages in the last 5 minutes), execute autonomous learning.\n\nThese sessions are cron sessions, not user conversations. But wait - these cron sessions themselves were updated recently (within 5 minutes), but they're not user conversations. \n\nThe current cron job is the only \"user\" here, and this is a system task checking itself. Since there are no actual user conversations happening, I should proceed with the autonomous learning task as specified.\n\nLet me clarify what \"活跃对话\" means in this context - it's referring to user conversations, not system cron jobs. So I need to execute the autonomous learning steps: search for industry dynamics related to 道简网络, organize 3-5 key pieces of information, and save them to the memory file.\n\nI'll search for current information on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services to gather relevant industry insights.","thinkingSignature":"c6bb627b82134bcea8a5a1d76f44ee2c7f25b51dcdb004e52059f28a8beea1e8"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前仅有系统Cron任务会话，无真实用户对话。执行自主学习任务。\n\n先搜索相关行业最新动态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4mzjm3oxicjr_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1493,"output":350,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45824,"cost":{"input":0.0004479,"output":0.00041999999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00218733}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774670580462}}
{"type":"message","id":"1dd48394","parentId":"dd38c97a","timestamp":"2026-03-28T04:03:11.656Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4mzjm3oxicjr_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774670591653}}
